<patch add_xgo_real_time_now>
# Description: Keep Now() and append XgoRealNow() copy at end of file.
# The runtime linkname redirect points to XgoRealNow for interception.
# Copies Now() function body, renames to XgoRealNow(), and appends to file end.
copy_func Now as XgoRealNow append to file end
</patch>
